<section id="about">
  <h3>About the Project</h3>
  <p>
    The DAKODA project focuses on building and exploring a learner-corpus
    infrastructure with standardized formats (CAS) and annotated datasets across
    multiple corpora. This infrastructure supports advanced linguistic research
    as well as the development of tools and resources for German L2 learner data.
  </p>
</section>

<section id="corpora">
  <h3>Corpora Overview</h3>
  <p>
    A variety of corpora are integrated into the DAKODA infrastructure,
    representing different modalities, tasks, and learner types. For
    corpus-specific metadata and download options, visit the
<a href="/repository.en.html">Repository</a>

  </p>
</section>

